<!-- Start of OSCAR Bundle Documentation -->
<hr width="100%" size="2">
<h1><i><a name="smsservlet"></a><font color="#0000aa">smsservlet.jar</font></i></h1>

<p>
<b>Description</b><br>
This bundle provides a front-end HTTP servlet to <code>smssender.jar</code> bundle that send SMS (Short Message Service) messages<br>
For more details on how to use this bundle, refer to the /doc/readme.html file embedded in the bundle jarfile and to smssender.jar embedded documentation.<br>
</p>

<p>
<b>Contributors</b><br>
Didier Donsez (<a href="mailto:Didier.Donsez@ieee.org">Didier.Donsez@ieee.org</a>)<br>
</p>

<p>
<b>License</b><br>
LGPL<br>
</p>

<p>
<b>Services</b><br>
None
</p>

<p>
<b>Properties</b><br>
None<br>
</p>

<p><b>Requirements</b><br>
servlet.jar<br>
1 or more services <code>org.osgi.service.http.HttpService</code> provided by <code>http.jar</code><br>
1 or more services <code>fr.imag.adele.bundle.sms.SMSSender</code> provided by <code>smssender.jar</code><br>
servicebinder.jar (to automate <code>org.osgi.service.http.HttpService</code> and <code>fr.imag.adele.bundle.sms.SMSSender</code> references)<br>
</p>

<!-- End of OSCAR Bundle Documentation -->

<hr width="100%" size="2">

